Package: b2program
Architecture: all
Depends: default-jre-headless | java-runtime-headless, ${misc:Depends}
Description: high-level code generator for formal B machines
 B2Program generates source code from high-level formal B machines. It can emit
 Java, C++, Python, Rust and TypeScript, allowing executable artefacts to be
 derived from verified B models.
 .
 This package installs the B2Program fat jar built from a pinned upstream commit
 together with a "b2program" launcher.
